      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALERT BAY (7) is a lightly-raced but progressive colt yet to miss a place. Produced a big effort for second in a NSW Derby heat when last seen at this circuit and distance. That was 11 weeks ago but he should be ready for the return having won a recent trial here. MESSAGE BANK (8) has relished a class drop in scoring easy wins in his last two outings. Yet to win here and draws wide but his confidence will be high. BETTORLEFTALONE (6) added to a string of wins and placings when he came from a similar barrier for third to Oaks runner-up Senses last week. Go well again. SOHO PIASTRI (5) led to win at this circuit and distance two back and was brave in a decent line-up at Bathurst last start, racing three wide without cover but sticking on for second. Respect.",
